<s-1 id="RM000000Z1U001X_01_0005" proc-id="RM0250U___00004C500000">
<ptxt>INSPECT INPUT SHAFT</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a V-block and dial indicator, inspect the shaft for runout.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C069620" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Maximum runout</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt> 0.03 mm (0.0012 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If runout exceeds the maximum, replace the input shaft.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a micrometer, measure the outside diameter of the input shaft journal surface.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C092870E02" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Outside diameter mm (in.)</title>
